Package sting

This package contains annotations used by the annotation processor to generate the DI container.

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Dependency
    Annotation used to describe the dependency.
    Fragment
    Annotates an interface that contributes to the object graph.
    Injectable
    Identifies an injectable type.
    Injector
    Annotates an interface or abstract class for which a fully-formed, dependency-injected implementation is to be generated from the included object graph fragments.
    Provides
    Annotates instance methods of a fragment to create a provider method binding.

Package sting Description

This package contains annotations used by the annotation processor to generate the DI container.
